"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-pg-plans-to-downplay-its-corporate-name-in-ads-during-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  Published\\u00c2May 15, 2024, 05:27 AM  Updated\\u00c2May 15, 2024, 05:27 AM  NEW YORK - What is missing from the Paris 2024 Olympics?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 361, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4896389690898682e-15, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703099307, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 305, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Next_Entertainment_World\", \"score\": 0.99999293488958, \"rank\": 7.04790132741594e-06, \"text\": \"NEW\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Next_Entertainment_World\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Next_Entertainment_World\"}, {\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/York\", \"score\": 0.9999989624508014, \"rank\": 9.292812708524106e-07, \"text\": \"YORK\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/York\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/York\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A tear-jerking corporate advertising campaign from Procter &amp; Gamble saluting the mothers of athletes.\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The consumer products maker, one of the world's biggest ad spenders and a sponsor of the Olympics, is instead focusing its marketing at the Games on its individual brands including Pampers diapers, Gillette razors and Ariel detergent.\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 650, \"end\": 657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pampers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\"}, {\"begin\": 687, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariel_Motorcycles\", \"score\": 0.9991319338898529, \"rank\": 0.0007593261456309559, \"text\": \"Ariel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariel_Motorcycles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariel_Motorcycles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The move is a step-change for P&amp;G, whose prior Olympics advertising campaigns emphasized the values of the Cincinnati-based company, struck an emotional chord and were among the company's most successful by sales and views, according to the website of Wieden+Kennedy, the agency that worked on the commercials.\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the past, we have had both a P&amp;G and a brand focus, and this time we just really decided we are going to go focus, not 100%, but much more prominently, on brands,\\\" said P&amp;G chief brand officer Marc Pritchard.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1241, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's what consumers that we serve are familiar with.\\\"\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Procter &amp; Gamble has reduced its spending on Olympics advertising in the United States by 50% over the last several Games, after previously spending tens of millions of dollars with U.S. broadcaster NBCUniversal, Reuters reported last month.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997310779671832, \"rank\": 0.0002689943681976008, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1503, \"end\": 1515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.999999989114258, \"rank\": 1.0871175003646346e-08, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 1517, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999767617285, \"rank\": 2.3238225984703838e-08, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company is one of the biggest global marketers of consumer products by revenue, selling roughly $82 billion worth in its fiscal year ending June 30, 2023.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It spends about $8 billion annually on advertising.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pritchard said that for the upcoming Games, P&amp;G is launching advertising for more than 30 of its brands, more than ever before.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our message really is serving the Olympic and Paralympic athletes, their families and fans around the world,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 2012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a bit of an everyday focus on it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, P&amp;G marketing at European retailers will emphasize the idea that its products are \\\"everyday champions\\\" in household tasks, according to the company.\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The company's biggest marketing push is in Europe because it is the host region for the Games, Pritchard said.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sponsors of the International Olympic Committee (IOC), including P&amp;G, pay upwards of an estimated $100 million for the right to use the famous Olympic rings in their marketing materials, according to the Reuters report.\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2353, \"end\": 2390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2545, \"end\": 2552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999767617285, \"rank\": 2.3238225984703838e-08, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"P&amp;G launched its first ever corporate advertising campaign highlighting the company rather than the household products it makes for the 2010 Vancouver Olympics, according to Wieden+Kennedy.\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2702, \"end\": 2725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998617568, \"rank\": 1.3773770131634033e-10, \"text\": \"2010 Vancouver Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Winter_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The global, multi-year campaign, called \\\"Thank you, Mom,\\\" showed the sacrifices mothers around the world make to help their children become Olympic athletes, and the lessons they teach them, like sportsmanship.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sales of P&amp;G products in the U.S., its biggest market, and Europe have been strong this year even as consumers face record levels of inflation.\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 3116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But lower sales in China have overshadowed those gains.\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3136, \"end\": 3141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9997814756591221, \"rank\": 0.00019661757806266957, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"REUTERS  Olympics  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3173, \"end\": 3180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 3224, \"end\": 3232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3341, \"entities\": []}]}"